          - Inherit python-single-r1.eclass instead of python.eclass
                   python.eclass is deprecated.

          - Fix metadata.xml
                   For the Quarity Assurance.

          - other some fixes

          modified:   metadata.xml
          modified:   mozc-2.16.1924.102.ebuild
          modified:   mozc-2.16.2014.102.ebuild

  10 Feb 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> mozc-2.16.1924.102.ebuild,
  mozc-2.16.2014.102.ebuild:
  ut: Omit deprecated python.eclass. Add correct licenses.

  - Updated to use python-single-r1.eclass
           python.eclass is deprecated.
           We should call python-r1(*).eclass instead of python.eclass.

  - Fixed licenses
           Japanese WordNet(EJDIC) has a derivative license of
  "Princeton"(WordNet).
           The licenses of "Hatena Keywords" and "Nico Nico Pedia" is not
  clear,
          so *they can be "all-rights-reserved"* .
          Please edit your /etc/portage/package.license to install.
           See http://www.geocities.jp/ep3797/mozc_01.html

  - Fixed metadata.xml
           For the Quality Assurance.

          modified:   metadata.xml
          modified:   mozc-ut-2.16.2014.102.20150114.ebuild
          new file:   /licenses/wn-ja
          new file:   /profiles/license_groups

